---
// Three-column value proposition summary with monospace numbering
---

<section data-animate="stagger" class="w-full py-16 sm:py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h2 data-animate="fade-up" class="opacity-0 font-mono text-sm text-stone-600 mb-6">Project goals</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-12 sm:gap-8">
      <div data-animate="fade-up" class="opacity-0">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-stone-600 block mb-3" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/></svg>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-100 mb-2">Incredible DX</h3>
        <p class="text-base text-stone-400 leading-relaxed">A declarative API that helps humans and agents get things right the first time.</p>
      </div>
      <div data-animate="fade-up" class="opacity-0">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-stone-600 block mb-3" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20"/><path d="M2 12h20"/></svg>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-100 mb-2">Fully open source</h3>
        <p class="text-base text-stone-400 leading-relaxed">No vendor lock-in. Designed to self-host. Deploy to a VPS or on bare metal at home.</p>
      </div>
      <div data-animate="fade-up" class="opacity-0">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-stone-600 block mb-3" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z"/></svg>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-100 mb-2">Fast, reactive, and multiplayer</h3>
        <p class="text-base text-stone-400 leading-relaxed">Data lives on the device, can be edited offline, and stays in sync with others.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
